%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20plastic-free%20alternative%20to%20Tide%20Pods%20is%20one%20of%20the%20few%20eco-friendly%20detergents%20I've%20found%20that%20actually%20work%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20buy%20through%20our%20links%2C%20Business%20Insider%20may%20earn%20an%20affiliate%20commission.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-reviews-expertise-in-product-reviews%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELearn%20more%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20EC30%20laundry%20detergent%20swatch%20is%20in%20front%20of%20a%20box%20of%20the%20swatches%20and%20another%20swatch%20is%20in%20a%20laundry%20drum%20for%20a%20review%20of%20the%20EC30%20Laundry%20Detergent.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F624b3cb2e22adb0018d1f4f0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJenny%20McGrath%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20staged%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20revolt%20recently%20because%20the%20eco-friendly%20laundry%20detergent%20I%20bought%20left%20our%20clothes%20smelly.%20The%20laundry%20strips%20I%20had%20purchased%20didn't%20seem%20to%20actually%20clean%20anything.%20So%2C%20I've%20been%20looking%20for%20an%20environmentally%20friendly%20detergent%20that%20works.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fec30clean.com%2Flaundry-detergent%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EProcter%20%26amp%3B%20Gamble's%20EC30%3C%2Fa%3E%20waterless%20products%20line%20are%20meant%20to%20reduce%20carbon%20emissions%20by%20dramatically%20reducing%20the%20amount%20of%20space%20they%20take%20up%20when%20shipping.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20laundry%20detergent%20looks%20like%20small%20fabric%20swatches%20that%20start%20to%20dissolve%20the%20second%20they%20touch%20water.%20I%20used%20the%20detergent%20on%20a%20couple%20of%20loads%20of%20laundry%20to%20see%20how%20it%20works.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20EC30%20laundry%20swatch%20is%20similar%20to%20a%20detergent%20pod%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20box%20of%20EC30%20Laundry%20detergent%20swatches%20with%20a%20single%20swatch%20sitting%20in%20front%20of%20it.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F624b3f12d6d14200199f6c8a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJenny%20McGrath%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20reviewed%20laundry%20machines%20for%20years%2C%20I%20know%20that%20too%20much%20soap%20is%20bad%20for%20your%20clothes%20and%20machine.%20My%20hesitation%20with%20laundry%20pods%20is%20the%20inability%20to%20adjust%20the%20amount%20of%20detergent%20depending%20on%20the%20load%20size.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20load%20I%20did%20was%20pretty%20small%2C%20but%20there%20were%20no%20detergent%20bubbles%20left%20on%20the%20door%20after%20the%20wash%20(a%20telltale%20sign%20you've%20used%20too%20much%20soap).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20EC30%20fits%20in%20your%20machine's%20detergent%20dispenser%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20EC30%20laundry%20detergent%20swatch%20in%20a%20washing%20machine%20detergent%20dispenser.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F624b3f59d6d14200199f6c97%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJenny%20McGrath%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20to%20crumple%20the%20EC30%20swatch%20to%20fit%20it%20in%20the%20detergent%20dispenser.%20After%20the%20wash%2C%20there%20was%20no%20residue%20left%20in%20the%20compartment.%20Later%20I%20learned%20I%20was%20supposed%20to%20use%20the%20powder%20setting%20on%20my%20washer%2C%20so%20I%20was%20impressed%20it%20still%20worked.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20don't%20have%20a%20dispenser%20or%20the%20tab%20won't%20fit%2C%20you%20can%20put%20it%20in%20the%20drum.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20EC30%20laundry%20detergent%20got%20rid%20of%20stains%20and%20odors%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20same%20shirt%20before%20and%20after%20being%20washed%20with%20EC30%20laundry%20detergent.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F624b3f9dd6d14200199f6ca3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJenny%20McGrath%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20used%20my%20normal%20cold-water%20settings%20and%20was%20pleased%20with%20the%20results.%20I'd%20had%20a%20shirt%20sitting%20out%20that%20had%20a%20mysterious%20stain%20and%20smelled%20because%20of%20my%20usual%20laundry%20detergent's%20ineptness.%20It's%20now%20clean%20and%20lightly%20scented.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20bottom%20line%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20EC30%20laundry%20detergent%20swatch%20in%20a%20washing%20machine%20drum%20with%20clothes.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F624b495082200b001943fc22%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJenny%20McGrath%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20EC30%20laundry%20detergent%20is%20a%20great%2C%20though%20pricey%2C%20choice%20if%20you%20don't%20have%20much%20room%20to%20stock%20big%20bottles.%20At%20about%20%241%20a%20load%2C%20they're%20quite%20a%20bit%20more%20than%20the%20%240.25%20per%20load%20you%20can%20expect%20to%20pay%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-53765-20%26h%3D17f6aad23cd58cc82fb0620b69abf8c1c8956166b98440f9eacbe09b1d8a0a5a%26postID%3D624b3ebe0f65d84d6a4888d6%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fec30-laundry-detergent-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fww