%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erefill%20kits%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20towelettes%20and%20stain%20removers.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWoolite%3A%20six%20moist%20cleaning%20towelettes%20and%20three%20stain%20removal%20wipes%20for%20spot-treating%20hard-to-remove%20stains.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20kits%20are%20very%20similar%2C%20but%20the%20biggest%20difference%20is%20that%20Dryel%20kits%20include%20a%20reusable%20dryer%20bag.%20The%20soiled%20clothes%20are%20placed%20in%20the%20bag%20with%20the%20cleaning%20towelette%20before%20they%20are%20tumbled%20in%20the%20dryer.%20The%20Woolite%20towelettes%20are%20placed%20directly%20in%20the%20dryer%20with%20the%20clothes%20that%20need%20to%20be%20cleaned.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20than%20a%20kit%2C%20you'll%20need%20a%20tumble%20dryer%20(at%20home%20or%20the%20laundromat).%20I%20would%20also%20recommend%20that%20you%20have%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-41823-20%26h%3D6857067cb214bd08801537785ac7fb618d6ed95511d3e786e0b04740a9160690%26postID%3D61b8efc8f2a36b1ac9f42d27%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fhow-to-dry-clean-clothes-at-home%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fgo.skimresources.com%252F%253Fid%253D35871X943606%2526amp%253Bxs%253D1%2526amp%253Burl%253Dhttps%25253A%25252F%25252Fwww.walmart.com%25252Fip%25252FHomz-T-Leg-Adjustable-Steel-Top-Ironing-Board-Solid-Blue%25252F40497881%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esturdy%20ironing%20board%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-41823-20%26h%3D77fc50976de69d906a54f0b5906030bd6c276943dce0d8400858b8a21305abb0%26postID%3D61b8efc8f2a36b1ac9f42d27%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fhow-to-dry-clean-clothes-at-home%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FProfessional-Resistant-Stainless-Self-Cleaning-Thermostat%252Fdp%252FB07JVFZJT7%252Fref%253Dsr_1_4%253Fdchild%253D1%2526amp%253Bkeywords%253Dsteam%252Biron%2526amp%253Bqid%253D1586628337%2526amp%253Bsr%253D8-4%5C%22%3Esteam%20iron%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hobbylobby.com%2FFabric-Sewing%2FSewing-Quilting-Notions%2FGarment-Accessories%2FSheer-Pressing-Cloth%2Fp%2F80959974%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epressing%20cloth%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20structured%20garments%20to%20give%20them%20a%20more%20professional%20%26quot%3Bstraight-from-the-dry-cleaner%26quot%3B%20look.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20basic%20steps%20to%20using%20any%20of%20these%20two%20kits%20are%20to%20pre-treat%20stains%20and%20then%20tossing%20a%20few%20items%20of%20clothing%20into%20the%20dryer%20bag%20if%20you're%20using%20Dryel%20or%20directly%20into%20your%20dryer%20if%20you're%20using%20Woolite%20with%20the%20cleaning%20toilette.%20Set%20the%20timer%20according%20to%20the%20kit's%20instructions%2C%20and%20hang%20or%20lay%20the%20clothes%20out%20to%20dry%20afterward.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20experience%20using%20the%20Dryel%20bag%2C%20I%20find%20that%20the%20clothes%20are%20exposed%20to%20more%20steam%20and%20cleaning%20ingredients%2C%20so%20they%20come%20out%20fresher%20and%20with%20fewer%20wrinkles%20than%20using%20just%20a%20towelette%20alone%20in%20the%20dryer.%20In%20today's%20large%20dryers%2C%20the%20steam%20level%20vents%20away%20too%20quickly%20and%20doesn't%20activate%20the%20Woolite%20towelette's%20cleaning%20ingredients%20to%20penetrate%20the%20fibers%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Ch2%3ETips%20for%20successful%20at-home%20dry%20cleaning%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223340%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22doing%20laundry%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5e948f2a29d6d970f93a69d2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222505%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ERead%20the%20instructions.%20The%20steps%20are%20simple%20but%20if%20you%20don't%20follow%20them%20or%20try%20to%20clean%20your%20entire%20closet%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20you're%20not%20doing%20it%20right.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECheck%20each%20garment%20for%20stains%20before%20you%20place%20it%20in%20the%20bag%20or%20dryer.%20Spot-treat%20the%20stain%20and%20wait%20at%20least%2010%20minutes%20before%20you%20add%20it%20to%20the%20dryer%20so%20that%20the%20cleaner%20has%20time%20to%20begin%20breaking%20down%20the%20stain.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EClose%20zippers%20and%20secure%20buttons%20before%20cleaning%20to%20help%20garments%20hold%20their%20shape%20and%20prevent%20snags.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EGroup%20similar%20types%20of%20fabrics%20and%20colors%20together%20in%20the%20load.%20Don't%20place%20a%20heavy%20wool%20coat%20in%20the%20dryer%20with%20a%20delicate%20silk%20blouse.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EClean%20out%20the%20dryer%20lint%20filter%20before%20beginning%20the%20cycle%20to%20prevent%20overheating%20in%20the%20drum.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESet%20the%20dryer%20timer%20and%20don't%20forget%20to%20remove%20the%20clothes%20promptly%20when%20the%20cycle%20is%20finished.%20The%20longer%20they%20sit%20in%20the%20dryer%2C%20the%20more%20wrinkled%20they%20will%20be.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhen%20the%20dryer%20cycle%20stops%2C%20immediately%20hang%20the%20garments%20or%20lay%20knitted%20items%20flat.%20They%20will%20be%20damp%20and%20need%20some%20time%20to%20dry%20completely.%20Do%20not%20wear%20clothes%20until%20they%20are%20fully%20dry%20to%20prevent%20set-in%20wrinkles.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fhow-to-dry-clean-clothes-at-home%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1777263691000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5e9742ccd