y%20products%20with%20sustainable%20materials%20and%20clean%20manufacturing%20processes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22frea%40insider.com%20(Francesca%20Rea)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20to%20clean%20your%20fabric%20face%20mask%20between%20trips%20to%20the%20store%20for%20essentials%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20buy%20through%20our%20links%2C%20Business%20Insider%20may%20earn%20an%20affiliate%20commission.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-reviews-expertise-in-product-reviews%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELearn%20more%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221140%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22how%20to%20clean%20a%20face%20mask%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5eda75f23f73707b1b2137b3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22855%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EEtsy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20data-analytics-module%3D%5C%22summary_bullets%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fcoronavirus%2F2019-ncov%2Fprevent-getting-sick%2Fcloth-face-cover.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECDC%20recommends%3C%2Fa%3E%20wearing%20a%20face%20mask%20in%20public%20to%20prevent%20community%20transmission%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20data-analytics-module%3D%5C%22summary_bullets%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%2220%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcoronavirus-live-updates-latest-news%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECOVID-19%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20order%20to%20maximize%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20wearing%20a%20face%20mask%2C%20it's%20important%20to%20keep%20it%20clean%2C%20be%20it%20via%20machine-%20or%20hand-washing.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIf%20someone%20in%20your%20home%20is%20ill%20or%20has%20a%20compromised%20immune%20system%2C%20you%20may%20want%20to%20add%20a%20disinfectant%20to%20the%20wash%2C%20as%20well.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fcoronavirus%2F2019-ncov%2Fprevent-getting-sick%2Fdiy-cloth-face-coverings.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECenters%20for%20Disease%20Control%20and%20Prevention%3C%2Fa%3E%20(CDC)%20has%20recommended%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fhow-to-double-mask%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewearing%20face%20masks%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20prevent%20the%20transmission%20of%20COVID-19%2C%20and%20with%20disposable%20masks%20in%20short%20supply%2C%20it's%20important%20to%20know%20how%20to%20handle%20and%20clean%20reusable%20cloth%20masks%20correctly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20spoke%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.taniaelliottmd.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETania%20Elliott%20MD%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20immunologist%20and%20national%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Facaai.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmerican%20College%20of%20Allergy%2C%20Asthma%2C%20and%20Immunology%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0who%20reiterated%20the%20importance%20of%20covering%20your%20face%20in%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMany%20people%20can%20be%20asymptomatic%20carriers%20of%20the%20virus%2C%20so%20you%20may%20have%20it%20and%20be%20spreading%20it%20without%20even%20knowing%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BTherefore%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fbest-face-masks-to-wear%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewearing%20a%20mask%3C%2Fa%3E%20protects%20others%20in%20the%20event%20that%20you%20sneeze%20or%20cough%20while%20you're%20talking%20and%20respiratory%20particles%20are%20transmitted%20into%20the%20air.%20And%20they%20should%20be%20worn%20whenever%20you%20cannot%20be%20more%20than%20six%20feet%20apart%20from%20people.%26quot%3B%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3ECan%20I%20clean%20my%20face%20mask%20at%20home%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDisposable%20masks%20and%20filters%20made%20from%20non-woven%20fibers%2C%20KN95%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fn95-mask-co-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EN95%20masks%3C%2Fa%3E%20cannot%20be%20safely%20cleaned%20at%20home.%20Exposure%20to%20excessive%20amounts%20of%20water%20and%20cleaning%20products%20will%20destroy%20the%20fibers%20and%20can%20damage%20the%20carbon%20filtration%20systems%20of%20N95%20respirators.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKN95%20or%20N95%20masks%20should%20be%20reserved%20for%20medical%20workers%2C%20but%20if%20you%20have%20one%2C%20know%20that%20they%20can%20be%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fniosh%2Ftopics%2Fhcwcontrols%2Frecommendedguidanceextuse.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworn%20up%20to%20five%20times%20by%20the%20same%20person%2C%20according%20to%20the%20CDC%3C%2Fa%3E.%20There%20are%20exceptions%20if%20the%20mask%20is%20used%20in%20certain%20medical%20procedures%2C%20damaged%2C%20or%20heavily%20soiled.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBecause%20of%20supply%20chain%20shortages%2C%20researchers%20have%20had%20to%20figure%20out%20if%20and%20how%20N95%20masks%20can%20be%20sanitized%20for%20reuse.%20Researchers%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Illinois%2C%20Urbana-Champaign%20found%20that%2050%20minutes%20of%20dry%20heat%20in%20an%20electric%20cooker%20such%20as%20an%20InstantPot%20can%20kill%20four%20types%20of%20viruses%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%228f9b4ced449618099f6ec1299a5d85c6%5C%22%20data-analytics-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%2240%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubs.acs.org%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1021%2Facs.estlett.0c00534%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EN95%20respirators%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20a%20coronavirus.%20After%20preheating%20the%20cooker%20for%20five%20minutes%20until%20it%20reaches%20347%20%C2%B0F%2C%20use%20a%20towel%20in%20the%20pot%20to%20line%20the%20interior%20and%20then%20place%20your%20mask%20on%20top%20for%2050%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EN95%20mask%20inventor%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Futrf.tennessee.edu%2Finformation-faqs-charged-filtration-material-performance-after-various-sterilization-techniques%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDr.%20Peter%20Tsai%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20scientists%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Tennessee%20are%20also%20studying%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20using%20ultraviolet-C%20(UV-C)%20light%20as%20a%20disinfectant.%20However%2C%20no%20procedures%20for%20cleaning%20these%20masks%20or%20filters%20at%20home%20have%20been%20approved.%20Fabric%20face%20masks%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20can%20and%20should%20be%20washed%20at%20home.%20They%20can%20be%20reused%20until%20they're%20torn%20or%20no%20longer%20fit%20the%20face%20of%20the%20wearer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EHow%20to%20wear%20and%20remove%20a%20face%20mask%20correctly%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20you%20put%20on%20a%20face%20mask%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiipf_042920_how-to-clean-a-face-mask-20%26h%3Dc181ce089e9b1c1e07f6306c2e21c8b5b20d9bf820e6e37dcc9c5fffcda8ba6d%26postID%3D61b8efc8f2a36b1ac9f42d77%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fhow-to-clean-sanitize-face-mask%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fgo.skimresources.com%252F%253Fid%253D35871X943606%2526amp%253Bxs%253D1%2526amp%253Burl%253Dhttps%25253A%25252F%25252Fwww.grove.co%25252Fcatalog%25252Fproduct%25252Fmrs-meyers-hand-soap%25252F%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewash%20your%20hands%20with%20soap%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20use%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fbest-hand-sanitizers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehand%20sanitizer%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Identify%20the%20exterior%20and%20interior%20sides%20of%20the%20mask.%20Always%20be%20sure%20to%20place%20the%20interior%20surface%20next%20to%20your%20skin.%20The%20mask%20should%20be%20worn%20tightly%20against%20the%20face%20and%20cover%20both%20your%20nose%20and%20mouth.%20Try%20not%20to%20touch%20the%20mask%20while%20you%20are%20wearing%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20is%20time%20to%20remove%20the%20mask%2C%20slip%20the%20elastic%20bands%20from%20your%20ears%2C%20or%20untie%20the%20strings.%20Do%20not%20grab%20the%20front%20of%20the%20mask%20to%20remove%20it%20from%20your%20face.%20Using%20the%20strings%20or%20elastic%20bands%2C%20place%20the%20mask%20directly%20in%20a%20paper%20bag%20for%20disposal%2C%20or%20to%20hold%20it%20until%20you're%20ready%20to%20wash%20or%20wear%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWash%20your%20hands%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Ch2%3EHow%20to%20clean%20a%20cloth%20face%20mask%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr.%20Elliott%20recommends%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fhow-to-clean-face-masks%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecleaning%20cloth%20masks%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0after%20each%20use.%20It's%20a%20good%20idea%20to%20have%20several%20masks%20on%20hand%20that%20can%20be%20rotated%2C%20so%20a%20clean%20one%20is%20always%20readily%20available.%20If%20you%20need%20to%20buy%20some%20extras%2C%20here%20are%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fbest-face-masks-to-wear%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20best%20face%20masks%20we've%20worn%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fwhere-to-buy-fashion-face-masks-online%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eface%20masks%20from%20apparel%20and%20retail%20brands%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fetsy-face-masks%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEtsy's%20highest-rated%20options%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20our%20favorites%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Ffitness%2Fbest-masks-for-working-out%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efor%20running%20and%20working%20out%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECloth%20masks%20can%20be%20machine-washed%20or%20hand-washed.%20When%20handling%20soiled%20masks%2C%20it's%20a%20good%20idea%20to%20wear%20disposable%20gloves%20and%20keep%20the%20masks%20away%20from%20your%20face.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIf%20the%20mask%20has%20a%20pocket%20that%20holds%20a%20removable%20non-woven%20filter%2C%20remove%20the%20filter%20before%20washing%20the%20mask.%20If%20you%20are%20using%20a%20folded%20bandana%20or%20scarf%20that%20has%20detachable%20elastic%20ear%20bands%2C%20remove%20those%20as%20well.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiipf_042920_how-to-clean-a-face-mask-20%26h%3Dffb7a71d8a1f148599fd876f48ed6df9c8ee9796b508f922a4e33d17a1a48843%26postID%3D61b8efc8f2a36b1ac9f42d77%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fhow-to-clean-sanitize-face-mask%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252Fgp%252Fproduct%252FB01D58R1BE%252Fref%253Das_li_ss_tl%253Fie%253DUTF8%2526amp%253BlinkCode%253Dll1%2526amp%253Btag%253Dbiipf_042920_how-to-clean-a-face-mask-20%2526amp%253BlinkId%253D310fe4d8c64711362b2c5a285764ca5f%2526amp%253Blanguage%253Den_US%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target