ill%20come%20a%20day%20when%20you%20need%20a%20specific%20set%20of%20clean%20clothes%20the%20next%20day%20but%20your%20parents%20aren't%20around%20and%20neither%20is%20a%20washing%20machine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20time%20to%20handwash%20your%20clothes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20clothes%20can%20be%20washed%20by%20hand%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAny%20clothing%20that%20is%20labeled%20as%20machine-washable%20can%20be%20hand-washed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20includes%20clothing%20made%20with%20cotton%2C%20synthetic%20knits%2C%20cotton%2Fpolyester%20blends%2C%20and%20microfiber.%20Even%20though%20bras%2C%20delicate%20lingerie%2C%20or%20lace%20blouses%20may%20be%20labeled%20as%20machine-washable%2C%20they%20will%20last%20longer%20and%20hold%20their%20shape%20better%20if%20they're%20hand-washed.%20Even%20if%20you%20only%20use%20the%20gentle%20cycle%20in%20a%20washer%2C%20hand-washing%20is%20less%20harmful%20than%20the%20agitation%20and%20spinning%20forces%20in%20a%20washer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20garments%20that%20have%20a%20%26quot%3Bdry%20clean%26quot%3B%20label%20can%20be%20hand-washed.%20This%20would%20include%20unstructured%20wool%20and%20cashmere%20sweaters%2C%20silk%20blouses%20and%20scarves%2C%20and%20rayon%20garments.%20Use%20a%20gentle%20detergent%20that's%20recommended%20for%20handwashing%2C%20cool%20water%20temperatures%2C%20and%20careful%20washing%20motions%20for%20any%20clothes%20labeled%20as%20such.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20if%20a%20garment%20has%20a%20%26quot%3Bdry%20clean%20only%26quot%3B%20label%2C%20believe%20it.%20The%20clothing%20may%20have%20an%20inner%20structure%20or%20lining%20(like%20a%20wool%20suit%20coat)%20that%20can't%20stand%20up%20to%20water.%20The%20fabric%20may%20also%20not%20have%20been%20pre-shrunk%20or%20treated%20to%20be%20colorfast.%20Take%20those%20garments%20to%20a%20professional%20dry%20cleaner%20unless%20you're%20willing%20to%20risk%20their%20ruin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EHow%20to%20was