ss%20Insider%20may%20earn%20an%20affiliate%20commission.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-reviews-expertise-in-product-reviews%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELearn%20more%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221885%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Carpet%20stain%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5ee7c02c4dca681c006a99fb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAndreyPopov%20%2F%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECleaning%20wool%20rugs%20is%20simple%20if%20you%20treat%20stains%20promptly%20and%20use%20the%20right%20types%20of%20cleaners.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWith%20the%20products%20provided%20in%20our%20list%20below%2C%20you%20can%20clean%20and%20restore%20your%20wool%20rugs%20to%20their%20natural%20beauty.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESee%20more%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-area-rug%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20best%20places%20to%20buy%20area%20rugs%20online%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhether%20you%20have%20a%20plush%20natural%20sheepskin%20rug%2C%20a%20vintage%2C%20handwoven%20Persian%20carpet%2C%20or%20a%20new%20machine-woven%20wool%20rug%2C%20you%20have%20a%20rug%20that%20will%20keep%20its%20beauty%20for%20decades%20if%20it%20is%20cleaned%20correctly.%20I%20have%20a%20large%20wool%20kilim%20rug%20that%20I%20have%20used%20for%20years%2C%20and%20it%20never%20seems%20to%20go%20out-of-style.%20I%20like%20wool%20because%20it%20is%20durable%2C%20it%20naturally%20repels%20stains%20and%20dust%20mites%2C%20and%20it%20is%20warm%20underfoot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20may%20shy%20away%20from%20wool%20because%20it%20is%20more%20expensive%20than%20man-made%20fibers%20and%20you%20think%20it%20is%20more%20difficult%20to%20maintain.%20(Think%20about%20all%20those%20wool%20sweaters%20you've%20had%20to%20hand-wash.)%20But%20with%20weekly%20vacuuming%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-vacuum%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egood%20vacuum%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20has%20a%20carpet%20beater%20bar%20(we%20recommend%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiipf_061520_how-to-clean-wool-carpet-20%26h%3D823b49163f99d4e48caf7bd2919aebc9edc798cbb9c791b3f273c7c46e1eda3c%26postID%3D61b8efc8f2a36b1ac9f42e58%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fhow-to-clean-a-wool-rug%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fgo.redirectingat.com%252F%253Fid%253D35871X943606%2526amp%253Burl%253Dhttps%25253A%25252F%25252Fwww.walmart.com%25252Fip%25252FShark-Navigator-Lift-Away-Bagless-Upright-Vacuum-Cleaner-NV351%25252F15528564%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShark%20Navigator%20Lift-Away%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0as%20the%20best%20budget%20option%C2%A0in%20our%20buying%20guide)%2C%20prompt%20treatment%20of%20stains%2C%20and%20a%20yearly%20cleaning%2C%20your%20investment%20will%20provide%20years%20of%20service%20and%20become%20more%20beautiful%20with%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere's%20a%20tip%20if%20your%20rug%20has%20fringed%20edges%3A%20Keep%20the%20powerful%20beater%20bar%20vacuums%20away%20from%20the%20fringe.%20Use%20a%20handheld%20vacuum%20or%20the%20upholstery%20brush%20on%20a%20wand%20to%20clean%20the%20fringe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20you%20put%20your%20new%20wool%20rug%20on%20the%20floor%2C%20put%20down%20the%20very%20best%20rug%20pad%20you%20can%20afford.%20The%20pad%20will%20reduce%20friction%20on%20the%20fibers%20and%20help%20your%20rug%20last%20longer.%20It%20will%20also%20add%20a%20bit%20of%20cushioning%20and%20protect%20the%20floors%20underneath%20the%20rug.%20I%20love%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiipf_061520_how-to-clean-wool-carpet-20%26h%3D37e19f8fc0f6cb9859216ac347bfaa5b3aa5bd0bbf2269ee1d99c7fb57a60102%26postID%3D61b8efc8f2a36b1ac9f42e58%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fhow-to-clean-a-wool-rug%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252Fgp%252Fproduct%252FB06WD1BZ78%252Fref%253Das_li_tl%253Fie%253DUTF8%2526amp%253Btag%253Dbiipf_061520_how-to-clean-wool-carpet-20%2526amp%253Bcamp%253D1789%2526amp%253Bcreative%253D9325%2526amp%253BlinkCode%253Das2%2526amp%253BcreativeASIN%253DB06WD1BZ78%2526amp%253BlinkId%253D9a65a3bfb3fd7799c1809a2be85a0d05%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERug%20Pad%20USA%20felt%20and%20rubber%20pads%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20are%20waterproof%2C%20safe%20for%20all%20types%20of%20floors%2C%20and%20my%20rugs%20never%20slip.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20remove%20stains%20from%20a%20wool%20rug%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20fabric%20care%20expert%20for%20more%20than%2040%20years%2C%20I%20can%20assure%20you%20that%20your%20life%20will%20be%20easier%20if%20when%20food%20or%20drink%20spills%20happen%2C%20you%20treat%20them%20as%20soon%20as%20possible.%20Always%20blot%20away%20liquids%20and%20lift%20away%20any%20solids%20%E2%80%94%20no%20rubbing!%20Rubbing%20only%20pushes%20the%20stain%20deeper%20into%20the%20fibers.%20The%20one%20exception%20to%20prompt%20treatment%20is%20muddy%20footprints.%20It%20is%20often%20better%20to%20allow%20the%20mud%20to%20dry%20and%20then%20vacuum%20it%20away%2C%20and%20then%20treat%20any%20residual%20stains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENever%20pour%20a%20carpet%20stain%20remover%20directly%20onto%20the%20carpet%3B%20some%20can%20cause%20wool%20dyes%20to%20bleed.%20Unless%20the%20stain%20remover%20states%20that%20it%20is%20safe%20for%20wool%2C%20proceed%20with%20caution.%20Never%20use%20a%20harsh%20cleaner%20like%20chlorine%20bleach%20or%20ammonia%20on%20wool%20that%20can%20damage%20the%20fibers.%3C%2Fp%3