t%20out%20dust.%20Don't%20forget%20to%20give%20the%20rug%20pad%20the%20same%20treatment.%20If%20the%20rug%20is%20too%20large%20to%20hang%2C%20vacuum%20it%20well%2C%20turn%20it%20over%20and%20then%20vacuum%20the%20back.%20Vacuum%20the%20pad%2C%20then%20remove%20it%20and%20vacuum%20the%20floor%20or%20carpet%20underneath.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIf%20you%20are%20working%20inside%2C%20to%20protect%20your%20flooring%20while%20you%20clean%20the%20rug%2C%20place%20a%20clean%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiipf_061520_how-to-clean-wool-carpet-20%26h%3D0c1c2f8093a8a4f742a2430e04863cbad06a406d0f7ce27f26045938bed526a2%26postID%3D61b8efc8f2a36b1ac9f42e58%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fhow-to-clean-a-wool-rug%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252Fgp%252Fproduct%252FB0053R2MEW%252Fref%253Das_li_tl%253Fie%253DUTF8%2526amp%253Btag%253Dbiipf_061520_how-to-clean-wool-carpet-20%2526amp%253Bcamp%253D1789%2526amp%253Bcreative%253D9325%2526amp%253BlinkCode%253Das2%2526amp%253BcreativeASIN%253DB0053R2MEW%2526amp%253BlinkId%253D2fc31d8a7edebf60d60bc0c03bacdd4d%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplastic%20tarp%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiipf_061520_how-to-clean-wool-carpet-20%26h%3Dbe7b5c997d642cb444fc175dc25ed23c18ac2daabf360293bac4388693c025c2%26postID%3D61b8efc8f2a36b1ac9f42e58%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fhow-to-clean-a-wool-rug%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252Fgp%252Fproduct%252FB01LPLJ0OY%252Fref%253Das_li_tl%253Fie%253DUTF8%2526amp%253Btag%253Dbiipf_061520_how-to-clean-wool-carpet-20%2526amp%253Bcamp%253D1789%2526amp%253Bcreative%253D9325%2526amp%253BlinkCode%253Das2%2526amp%253BcreativeASIN%253DB01LPLJ0OY%2526amp%253BlinkId%253D8e957d4d97a92399