ds).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20these%20gloves%20are%20plenty%20grippy%2C%20the%20silicone%20they're%20made%20of%20doesn't%20offer%20the%20best%20dexterity%2C%20and%20you'll%20have%20a%20hard%20time%20performing%20more%20delicate%20tasks%2C%20like%20operating%20grilling%20tools%20or%20handling%20a%20beverage%20while%20wearing%20them.%20They're%20also%20a%20little%20more%20cumbersome%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20storage%2C%20because%20they%20don't%20fold%20or%20roll%20up%20neatly%20(or%20at%20all)%20in%20the%20way%20that%20suede%20and%20cotton%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bottom%20line%20with%20these%20gloves%20is%20that%20if%20you're%20going%20to%20be%20careless%20with%20them%2C%20as%20in%20get%20them%20covered%20in%20grease%20or%20forget%20them%20beside%20the%20grill%20for%20a%20day%2C%20a%20month%2C%20or%20even%20a%20year%2C%20they'll%20withstand%20whatever%20weather%20may%20come%20(so%20long%20as%20they%20don't%20blow%20away).%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHow%20we%20test%20gloves%20for%20grilling%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Assortment%20of%20best%20grill%20gloves%20of%202023%20Insider%20tested%20laid%20out%20on%20a%20deck.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F609e94b567e41a001862217e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EOwen%20Burke%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20recently%20retested%20all%20of%20our%20picks%2C%20focusing%20on%20dexterity%20and%20heat%20resistance%20and%20retention.%20Since%20gloves%20are%20meant%20for%20active%20grilling%2C%20we%20considered%20how%20easy%20it%20was%20to%20grab%20and%20operate%20tongs%2C%20hold%20a%20beverage%2C%20tend%20to%20a%20fire%2C%20and%20adjust%20food%20over%20a%20fire.%20We%20then%20noted%20what%20happened%20to%20each%20glove%20after%20five%20seconds%20on%20glowing-hot%20coals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20spoke%20with%20author%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbarbecuebible.com%2Fbarbecue-university%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBarbecue%20University%20TV%3C%2Fa%3E%20host%2C%20and%20namesake%20of%20our%20favorite%20set%20of%20gloves%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.stevenraichlen.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESteven%20Raichlen%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20well%20as%20famed%20New%20York%20City-based%20meat%20purveyor%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flafrieda.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPat%20LaFrieda%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20learn%20what%20makes%20a%20great%20grilling%20glove.%20Both%20told%20us%20welding%20gloves%20were%20the%20way%20to%20go%2C%20and%20after%20testing%20various%20models%20in%20different%20materials%2C%20we%20agreed.%20LaFrieda%20and%20(obviously)%20Raichlen%20both%20noted%20that%20a%20longer%20cuff%20on%20a%20welding%20glove%20is%20ideal%20(hence%20Raichlen's%20decision%20to%20design%20his%20own%20pair).%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20in%20BBQ%20gloves%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere's%20what%20we%20looked%20for%20in%20our%20top%20picks%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHeat%20resistance%20and%20retention%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Your%20grill%20gloves%20are%20going%20to%20be%20exposed%20to%20high%20heat%20for%20varying%20lengths%20of%20time.%20We%20looked%20for%20gloves%20that%20didn't%20stay%20hot%20when%20exposed%20to%20glowing%20coals%2C%20and%20we%20noted%20which%20pairs%20developed%20burns%20or%20smudges.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPerformance%20and%20dexterity%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20It's%20important%20to%20be%20able%20to%20operate%20tools%20and%2C%20perhaps%2C%20keep%20your%20grip%20on%20a%20beverage%20while%20wearing%20grilling%20gloves.%20We%20noted%20whether%20or%20not%20we%20were%20able%20to%20maneuver%20easily%20within%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaterial%20quality%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We've%20kept%20each%20set%20of%20gloves%20outside%20for%20more%20than%20a%20year%20and%20looked%20over%20each%20glove%20for%20stitching%20defects%20or%20weak%20points%20where%20the%20gloves%20might%20begin%20to%20separate.%20We'll%20keep%20an%20eye%20on%20this%20going%20forward%20as%20we%20test%20for%20longevity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ELeather%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ELeather%20gloves%20are%20highly%20heat-resistant%20(up%20to%20about%20932%20degrees%20Fahrenheit%2C%20which%20is%20why%20welders%20use%20them)%2C%20and%20a%20good%20pair%20will%20last%20a%20long%20time.%20The%20downside%20of%20leather%20is%20that%20it's%20tough%20to%20clean%2C%20so%20it's%20not%20great%20for%20handling%20foods%20or%20coming%20into%20contact%20with%2C%20say%2C%20meat%20drippings.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESilicone%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESilicone%20isn't%20as%20heat-resistant%20as%20leather%20(up%20to%20about%20500%20degrees%20Fahrenheit)%2C%20but%20it%20is%20the%20most%20cleanable%20option%20and%20is%20great%20for%20lower-temperature%20smoking%20and%20handling%20meat.%20Some%2C%20like%20our%20waterproof%20pick%2C%20can%20even%20be%20run%20through%20the%20dishwasher.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EKevlar%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EKevlar%20is%20similarly%20heat-resistant%20to%20leather%20(up%20to%20about%20800%20degrees%20Fahrenheit)%2C%20but%20lighter%20in%20weight%20and%20often%20offers%20more%20mobility.%20It%20is%20also%20similarly%20difficult%20to%20clean%2C%20and%20not%20great%20for%20direct%20contact%20with%20food.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDesign%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20grill%20glove%20that%20can%20withstand%20temperatures%20exceeding%20500%20degrees%20Fahrenheit%20is%20a%20great%20idea%2C%20but%20if%20the%20cuffs%20are%20so%20short%20that%20your%20wrists%20and%20forearms%20are%20exposed%20while%20reaching%20over%20an%20open%20flame%2C%20what%20good%20are%20they%20really%3F%20Now%2C%20not%20all%20of%20us%20are%20getting%20so%20dangerousl