nk%20capacity%2C%20ice%20is%20evenly%20shaped%20across%20sizes%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBulky%2C%20small%20ice%20is%20on%20the%20thin%20side%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20three%20quarts%2C%20this%20ice%20maker's%20water%20tank%20had%20the%20largest%20capacity%20out%20of%20all%20the%20machines%20we%20tested.%20After%20running%20two%20small%20cycles%2C%20one%20medium%2C%20and%20one%20large%2C%20there%20were%20still%20over%20two%20quarts%20left.%20Regardless%20of%20the%20size%20you%20select%2C%20each%20ice%20cycle%20produces%20nine%20pieces%20of%20ice%20and%20takes%20under%2015%20minutes%20to%20complete.%20This%20speed%20is%20standard%20among%20ice%20makers%20with%20one%20or%20two%20sizes%2C%20but%20I%20was%20impressed%20by%20the%20NewAir's%20consistent%20timing%20in%20all%20three%20sizes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDraining%20the%20leftover%20water%20was%20easy%20because%20the%20NewAir's%20drainage%20port%20is%20conveniently%20located%20on%20its%20side%20near%20the%20bottom%2C%20as%20opposed%20to%20underneath%20the%20machine.%20If%20you%20shut%20off%20the%20machine%20mid-cycle%2C%20any%20ice%20formed%20will%20drop%20back%20into%20the%20water%20tank.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20small%20ice%20started%20losing%20shape%20just%20from%20the%20heat%20of%20my%20hand%3B%20the%20medium%20and%20large%20ice%20cubes%20were%20more%20substantial.%20However%2C%20this%20was%20the%20case%20for%20all%20of%20the%20ice%20makers%20I%20tested%2C%20so%20the%20NewAir%20kept%20its%20place%20as%20the%20best%20ice%20maker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22raw%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgiphy.com%2Fembed%2FwwPfn9DpD4IlYchxfR%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22raw%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgiphy.com