amaged%20appliances%20with%20energy-efficient%20ones%2C%20Pendleton%20says%20a%20home%20can%20sell%20for%202.6%25%20more%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zillow.com%2Fresearch%2Fhome-features-that-sell-2022-30822%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EZillow%20research%3C%2Fa%3E.%20On%20top%20of%20that%2C%20high-end%20professional%20appliances%20could%20net%20homeowners%20another%201.6%25%20sale%20premium.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fbest-refrigerator%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erefrigerators%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20stoves%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fbest-dishwasher%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edishwashers%3C%2Fa%3E%20come%20in%20standard%20sizes%20that%20will%20easily%20fit%20existing%20cabinetry%20and%20countertop%20cutouts.%20Pankonien%20says%20that%20many%20of%20her%20clients%20are%20swapping%20standard-depth%20refrigerators%20for%20counter-depth%20models%20to%20create%20a%20seamless%20profile%20with%20existing%20cabinetry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EReplace%20cabinet%20fronts%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22White%20shaker%20style%20kitchen%20cabinets%20are%20shown%20beside%20a%20stainless%20steel%20stove.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6320aa6be8b50000185105d4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221124%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EFotografia%20Inc.%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGutting%20your%20kitchen%20cabinets%20and%20replacing%20them%20with%20a%20custom%20set%20is%20one%20of%20the%20more%20expensive%20projects%20you%20can%20tackle%20in%20a%20home.%20To%20save%20money%2C%20consider%20replacing%20the%20cabinet%20fronts%20for%20an%20updated%20look.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BReplacing%20your%20cabinet%20fronts%20from%20an%20arched%20or%20heavily%20detailed%20panel%20to%20a%20clean%20shaker%20style%20door%20is%20one%20of%20the%20more%20costly%20reno-free%20upgrades%2C%20but%20it%20will%20absolutely%20change%20the%20look%20of%20your%20entire%20kitchen%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Pankonien.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20classic%20shaker%20cabinet%20door%20appeals%20to%20the%20most%20buyers%2C%20and%20they%20could%20pay%202%25%20more%20than%20expected%20for%20a%20kitchen%20with%20shaker%20cabinets%2C%26quot%3B%20Pendleton%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20we%20like%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESwap%20out%20hardware%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221198%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Black%20rectangular%20cabinet%20pulls%20are%20shown%20on%20the%20gray%20cupboards%20and%20island%20of%20a%20kitchen.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6320ab29e8b5000018510635%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22899%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ELowe's%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20one%20is%20super%20easy.%20%26quot%3BNew%20pulls%20and%20knobs%20can%20give%20a%20kitchen%20a%20whole%20new%20feel%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Pendleton.%20%26quot%3BMatte%20black%20is%20associated%20with%20a%202%25%20sale%20premium%2C%20while%20unlacquered%20brass%20hardware%20will%20give%20your%20kitchen%20a%20softer%2C%20classic%20look.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20not%20ready%20for%20a%20splurge%2C%20Dunford%20suggests%20removing%20the%20current%20hardware%20and%20giving%20it%20a%20fresh%20finish%20with%20a%20coat%20of%20spray%20paint.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EReplace%20builder-grade%20light%20fixtures%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20gold%20Sputnik%20style%20chandeliers%20hang%20above%20a%20blue%20kitchen%20island.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6320ab9889d2b3001894d969%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Home%20Depot%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELight%20fixtures%20contribute%20to%20the%20overall%20look%20and%20feel%20of%20a%20room%2C%20and%20multiple%20sources%20of%20light%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20overhead%20%E2%80%94%20play%20a%20key%20part%20in%20both%20visual%20aesthetics%20and%20utility.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThink%20about%20layering%20your%20fixtures%20so%20light%20is%20diffused%20from%20different%20angles%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Pendtleton.%20%26quot%3BCombining%20a%20ceiling%20fixture%20with%20pendants%2C%20sconces%2C%20and%20under-cabinet%20lighting%20will%20give%20you%20the%20most%20functional%2C%20flattering%20light%20in%20the%20kitchen.%26quot%3B%20She%20adds%20that%20LED%20fixtures%20and%20lightbulbs%20can%20boost%20your%20selling%20price%20by%201.9%25.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20kitchen%20with%20brass%20fixtures%2C%20Dunford%20says%20that%20warmer%20lighting%20pairs%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EInstall%20open%20shelving%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Three%20different%20rustic%20pine%20shelves%20hold%20bowls%2C%20glasses%2C%20and%20plates.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6320ac4f89d2b3001894d985%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EWest%20Elm%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPankonien%20loves%20incorporating%20open%20shelving%20into%20almost%20every%20kitchen%20space%20she%20works%20on.%20%26quot%3BStyled%20with%20glassware%2C%20plates%2C%20decorative%20pitchers%2C%20and%20small%20art%2C%20it's%20an%20easy%20way%20to%20create%20a%20well-designed%20focal%20point%20that%20is%20also%20super%20functional%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20Plus%2C%20open%20shelving%20is%20a%20more%20affordable%20alternative%20to%20replacing%20cabinets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20gets%20better%20though.%20%26quot%3BZillow%20research%20finds%20this%20easy%20DIY%20project%20made%20popular%20by%20home%20improvement%20TV%20shows%20can%20boost%20a%20home's%20value%20by%201.5%25%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Pendleton.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDunford%20adds%20that%20kitchens%20where%20everything%20is%20hidden%20in%20cabinets%20are%20dwindling%20in%20popularity.%20%26quot%3BInstead%20of%20putting%20everything%20away%2C%20bring%20in%20earthenware%2C%20bowls%2C%20and%20plates%2C%20and%20pretty%20wooden%20spoons%20to%20display%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20layering%20wood%20cutting%20boards%20is%20impactful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFreshen%20up%20with%20a%20coat%20of%20paint%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20large%20kitchen%20with%20gray-white%20walls%2C%20white%20cabinets%20and%20black%20countertops%20is%20shown.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6320acc889d2b3001894d9a8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESherwin-Williams%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20fresh%20coat%20of%20paint%20will%20do%20wonders%20for%20any%20room%2C%20but%20for%20kitchens%20in%20particular%2C%20Pendleton%20has%20seen%20a%20trend%20in%20resale%20value.%20%26quot%3BZillow's%20latest%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zillowgroup.com%2Fnews%2Fpaint-colors-that-could-lead-to-higher-offers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einterior%20paint%20color%20analysis%3C%2Fa%3E%20finds%20buyers%20are%20drawn%20to%20light%20and%20bright%20kitchens%20with%20off-white%20or%20tan%20kitchen%20walls%20scoring%20the%20highest%20with%20potential%20buyers%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20A%20white%20kitchen%20can%20add%20as%20much%20as%20%24700%20to%20the%20sales%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPankonien%20agrees%20that%20updating%20kitchen%20walls%20and%20cabinetry%20with%20a%20coat%20of%20white%20paint%20gives%20a%20beautiful%20lift%20to%20a%20space.%20It's%20also%20a%20great%20opportunity%20to%20infuse%20lightness%20while%20also%20turning%20your%20kitchen%20into%20a%20clean%20slate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EReplace%20the%20faucet%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20person%20is%20rinsing%20a%20spoon%20under%20water%20running%20from%20a%20brass%20Delta%20kitchen%20faucet.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6320ad4289d2b3001894d9ba%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221124%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EReplacing%20your%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fbest-kitchen-faucet%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ekitchen%20faucet%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20an%20easy%2C%20affordable%20upgrade%2C%20according%20to%20Pankonien.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20great%20opportunity%20to%20bring%20in%20a%20brass%20or%20black%20finish%20to%20your%20kitchen%2C%20which%20can%20dramatically%20update%20the%20overall%20look%20of%20your%20space%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20%26quot%3BPlus%2C%20there%20have%20never%20been%20more%20beautiful%20options%20in%20this%20category.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMake%20it%20a%20touchless%20faucet%20for%20a%20potential%200.7%25%20sale%20premium%2C%20as%20Zillow%20reporters%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fzillow.mediaroom.com%2F2020-06-22-The-End-of-Open-Floor-Plans-How-Homes-Will-Look-Different-After-Coronavirus%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebuyers%20increasingly%20look%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20smart%20features%20to%20help%20them%20keep%20their%20homes%20germ-free.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAdd%20a%20backsplash%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20white%20subway%20tile%20backsplash%20is%20shown%20with%20sugar%20canister%2C%20plates%2C%20and%20potted%20herbs%20in%20foreground.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6320adb3e8b500001851068d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EWall%20Pops%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPendleton%20says%20that%20a%20backsplash%20adds%20both%20style%20and%20functionality%20to%20a%20kitchen.%20%26quot%3BIt%20keeps%20oil%20and%20food%20splatters%20off%20the%20walls%20for%20an%20easier-to-clean%20kitchen%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20%26quot%3BPlus%2C%20it%20could%20add%200.6%25%20to%20your%20bottom%20line%20when%20it%20comes%20time%20to%20sell.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPankonien%20likes%20a%20clean%20subway%20backsplash%20for%20visual%20texture%20and%20easy%20coordination%20with%20any%20countertop.%20%26quot%3BWe%20also%20love%20pairing%20a%20dark%20cabinet%20color%20with%20a%20coordinating%20dark%20subway%20tile%20for%20instant%20style%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20For%20a%20quick%2C%20affordable%20backsplash%20fix%2C%20try%20removable%20peel-and-stick%20tile.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBring%20in%20a%20standalone%20island%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20brown%20antiqued%20kitchen%20island%20is%20shown%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20kitchen%20with%20the%20sink%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6320adfbe8b50000185106a5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EWayfair%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20opting%20for%20all%20matching%20cabinetry%2C%20consider%20a%20kitchen%20island%20that%20looks%20and%20feels%20like%20a%20piece%20of%20furniture%20rather%20than%20just%20an%20extension%20of%20your%20kitchen%20cabinets.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20add%20soul%20and%20character%20to%20your%20kitchen%2C%20try%20topping%20a%20vintage%20table%20with%20a%20new%20stone%20countertop%2C%26quot%3B%20Pendleton%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20homes%20with%20kitchen%20islands%20can%20sell%20for%200.3%25%20more%20than%20expected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ECreate%20interest%20with%20window%20treatments%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5