er.com%2F62a8ebdd6053710019ea3ddb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221124%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJames%20Osmond%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EReplacing%20dated%20cabinet%20hardware%20is%20one%20of%20the%20easiest%20and%20highest-impact%20upgrades%20you%20can%20make%20to%20a%20rental.%20Just%20unscrew%20the%20pulls%20or%20knobs%20with%20a%20screwdriver%20or%20drill%2C%20and%20screw%20on%20the%20new%20ones.%20I%20saved%20all%20the%20original%20cabinet%20hardware%20in%20my%20apartment%20in%20a%20zip-top%20bag%2C%20so%20when%20it's%20time%20to%20move%20out%2C%20I%20can%20put%20the%20old%20ones%20back%20and%20bring%20the%20new%20ones%20with%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAdd%20a%20peel-and-stick%20backsplash%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20silver%20backsplash%20with%20an%20intricate%20scroll%20design%20covers%20the%20wall%20behind%20a%20kitchen%20sink.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62fbcc99c87abe0018c2bc70%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EWall%20Pops%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20your%20rental%20kitchen%20has%20an%20unsightly%20backsplash%20or%20is%20without%20one%20entirely%2C%20a%20peel-and-stick%20backsplash%20is%20a%20temporary%20way%20to%20customize%20your%20kitchen.%20These%20backsplashes%20are%20typically%20made%20of%20thick%20vinyl%20so%20you%20can%20easily%20trim%20them%20with%20a%20pair%20of%20scissors.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20installing%20the%20backsplash%20near%20the%20stove%2C%20it%20should%20be%20rated%20for%20long-term%20heat%20exposure%20or%20placed%2015%20inches%20above%20the%20stovetop%20for%20breathing%20room.%20To%20prevent%20mold%20from%20accumulating%20behind%20the%20peel-and-stick%20tile%2C%20make%20sure%20the%20surface%20is%20completely%20dry%20before%20installation%20and%20keep%20moisture%20away%20from%20the%20finished%20project.