Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20with%20most%20viral%20trends%2C%20it's%20fun%20to%20see%20if%20they%20actually%20work%20in%20real%20life.%20Cue%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-56046-20%26h%3D783fec913991c6b5a98341fbaa928e261863b32d95b9cd73b9e5a41fede04fdb%26postID%3D62b9e70e056870737a38e6f6%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fzep-grout-cleaner-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252Fdp%252FB07PB6K5PZ%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EZep%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20grout%20cleaner%20and%20brightener.%20People%20claim%20it%20takes%20years%20off%20old%20grout%2C%20lifts%20heavy%20stains%2C%20and%20works%20in%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20decided%20to%20try%20Zep%20on%20the%20grout%20of%20the%20porcelain%20floor%20tile%20in%20my%20bathroom.%20The%20bathroom%20was%20renovated%20a%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20before%20I%20moved%20in%2C%20so%20I%20estimate%20that%20it's%20about%20four%20years%20old.%20I'll%20start%20by%20saying%20that%20cleaning%20the%20bathroom%20is%20my%20least%20favorite%20chore%2C%20but%20using%20Zep%20for%20this%20review%20made%20it%20a%20little%20more%20tolerable.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EOur%20review%20of%20Zep%20Grout%20Cleaner%20and%20Brightener%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-56046-20%26h%3D783fec913991c6b5a98341fbaa928e261863b32d95b9cd73b9e5a41fede04fdb%26postID%3D62b9e70e056870737a38e6f6%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fzep-grout-cleaner-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252Fdp%252FB07PB6K5PZ%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EZep%20Grout%20Cleaner%20and%20Brightener%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20bleach-free%20grout%20cleaner%20that%20is%20easy%20to%20use%20and%20requires%20very%20little%20scrubbing.%20It%20can%20be%20used%20on%20white%20or%20colored%20grout%20lines%20and%20is%20said%20to%20lift%20tough%20stains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20often%20with%20typical%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-bathroom-cleaning-products%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebathroom%20cleaners%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20bleach%20fumes%20they%20emit%20during%20use%20are%20extremely%20intense%2C%20especially%20in%20a%20small%20space%20like%20a%20bathroom.%20Not%20so%20with%20Zep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20entire%20cleaning%20experience%20was%20so%20much%20more%20tolerable%20without%20the%20smell%20of%20bleach%20wafting%20through%20the%20air%3B%20rather%2C%20Zep%20consists%20of%20mostly%20hydrochloric%20acid%2C%20alcohol%2C%20and%20water.%20Rubber%20gloves%20are%20recommended%20during%20use.%20While%20it%20is%20good%20for%20floors%20like%20porcelain%20and%20ceramic%2C%20it%20is%20not%20recommended%20for%20use%20on%20marble%2C%20terrazzo%2C%20travertine%2C%20natural%20stone%2C%20or%20stainless%20steel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2288ec746f-cfa2-4003-8b9c-66a83b753c4f%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22The%20application%20process%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20application%20process%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221704%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Clear%20liquid%20in%20a%20bottle%20with%20the%20text%20%E2%80%9CZep%E2%80%9D%20is%20being%20poured%20out%20onto%20tile%20floor.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62b9e7a0a8ac190019a7bc76%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221278%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20applied%20Zep%20Grout%20Cleaner%20directly%20to%20the%20grout%20lines.%3Cp%3EBrenna%20Darling%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20used%20a%20broom%20to%20do%20a%20quick%20sweep%20of%20my%20bathroom%20to%20remove%20dust%2C%20hair%2C%20and%20debris.%20Then%20I%20squirted%20Zep%20directly%20onto%20all%20the%20grout%20lines%2C%20no%20brush%20needed%20at%20that%20point.%20Zep%20recommends%20application%20to%20grout%20lines%20only%2C%20so%20I%20tried%20my%20best%20not%20to%20get%20it%20on%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20tile.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20could%20immediately%20see%20the%20solution%20bubbling%20up%20on%20the%20extra%20dirty%20areas%2C%20which%20indicated%20to%20me%20that%20it%20was%20lifting%20up%20those%20tougher%20stains%20right%20away.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221704%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20black%20round%20timer%20set%20to%20three%20minutes%20is%20lying%20face%20up%20on%20tile%20floor.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62b9eaaef921d300180390ef%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221278%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EZep%20recommends%20letting%20the%20cleaner%20do%20its%20work%20for%20three%20minutes.%3Cp%3EBrenna%20Darling%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20let%20it%20sit%20for%20the%20recommended%20three%20minutes.%20Then%20I%20scrubbed%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-56046-20%26h%3Db2457786772d90499bca1a95b4fada40945cf09505da4bc3955a8e75669a8206%26postID%3D62b9e70e056870737a38e6f6%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fzep-grout-cleaner-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.lowes.com%252Fpd%252FScotch-Brite-511P-12-CC-Grout-Brush-12-1%252F1002916628%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrout%20scrubbie%20brush%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20any%20regular%20cleaning%20brush%20would%20have%20worked%20just%20fine.%20Afterward%2C%20I%20wiped%20all%20of%20the%20product%20up%20using%20a%20paper%20towel%2C%20then%20finished%20with%20a%20damp%20cloth%20to%20ensure%20full%20removal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221704%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20hand%20is%20holding%20a%20black%20and%20wh