TikTok.%20What%20I%20got%20was%20a%20super%20clean%20floor%20with%20grout%20lines%20that%20were%20a%20few%20shades%20lighter.%20It's%20very%20possible%20my%20grout%20was%20originally%20light%20gray%2C%20and%20perhaps%20the%20viral%20videos%20feature%20much%20dirtier%20grout%20than%20I%20had.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20other%20downside%20is%20that%20there%20is%20a%20decent%20number%20of%20materials%20that%20Zep%20should%20not%20be%20used%20on.%20Be%20sure%20to%20read%20the%20label%20and%20make%20sure%20it's%20safe%20to%20use%20on%20your%20floor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22002a24c6-a053-4e37-aa33-eb28cf1ed353%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22The%20bottom%20line%5C%22%3EThe%20bottom%20line%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegardless%20of%20a%20dramatic%20grout%20color%20transformation%20or%20not%2C%20Zep%20is%20hands%20down%20the%20best%20grout%20cleaner%20I've%20used.%20I%20was%20impressed%20with%20how%20simple%20it%20was%20to%20use%20and%20how%20well%20it%20lifted%20the%20dirt%20from%20the%20grout.%20It%20took%20less%20than%2010%20minutes%20and%20I%20didn't%20even%20need%20to%20scrub%20very%20hard.%20While%20my%20grout%20didn't%20completely%20change%20colors%2C%20it%20looked%20considerably%20brighter%20and%20significantly%20cleaner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20recommend%20Zep%20for%20anyone%20needing%20a%20good%20clean%20for%20their%20tile%20floors%20and%20for%20those%20who%20want%20to%20work%20smarter%2C%20not%20harder%20in%20their%20weekly%20chore%20routine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fzep-grout-cleaner-review%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1777262824000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62b9ecedf921d30018039161%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fzep-grout-cleaner-review%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20the%20results%20weren't%20absolutely%