of%20loose%20strands%20behind.%20For%20a%20long%20time%2C%20I%20let%20my%20hair%20work%20its%20way%20down%20the%20drain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20you%20judge%20my%20reckless%20habits%2C%20know%20that%20I%20tried%20to%20do%20better.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20I%20bought%20many%20shower%20drain%20covers%3A%20a%20cheap%20wire%20mesh%20one%20that%20collected%20soap%20scum%20and%20ultimately%20rusted%2C%20a%20flower-shaped%20hair%20catcher%20with%20suction%20cups%20that%20was%20impossible%20to%20clean%2C%20and%20a%20set%20of%20pretty%20pastel%20covers%20that%20developed%20a%20yellow%20hue%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENearly%20all%20did%20a%20decent%20job%20of%20catching%20hair%2C%20but%20they%20also%20created%20a%20dam%20that%20left%20me%20standing%20in%20a%20couple%20inches%20of%20soapy%20water.%20It%20became%20my%20habit%20to%20kick%20the%20cover%20aside%20mid-shower.%20And%20with%20that%2C%20baby%20Chewbaccas%20were%20frequently%20born%20from%20the%20depths%20of%20my%20drain%2C%20snaked%20out%20by%20myself%2C%20my%20reluctant%20partner%2C%20or%20the%20plumber%20sent%20by%20my%20landlord%20when%20it%20got%20%3Cem%3Ereally%3C%2Fem%3E%20bad%20(sorry%2C%20Murray).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20last%20resort%20was%20this%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-51044-20%26h%3Df258239bdb28a25c6f03894883191472eb4d460121706dd7e9307811eafb38f5%26postID%3D61b8efc8f2a36b1ac9f43608%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Foxo-shower-drain-cover-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.oxo.com%252Fsilicone-shower-tub-drain-protector.html%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOXO%20shower%20drain%20cover%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20couldn't%20imagine%20it%20would%20stay%20put%20because%20it%20lacked%20suction%20cups%2C%20but%20I%20gave%20it%20a%20try%20out%20of%20