you%20buy%20through%20our%20links%2C%20Business%20Insider%20may%20earn%20an%20affiliate%20commission.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-reviews-expertise-in-product-reviews%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELearn%20more%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22How%20to%20use%20a%20bidet%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5e73c0d4c48540042357a888%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EWalmart%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20it's%20time%20to%20shower%2C%20do%20you%20rub%20a%20dry%20towel%20all%20over%20yourself%20and%20call%20it%20a%20day%3F%20Of%20course%20not.%20Yet%2C%20using%20dry%20toilet%20paper%20is%20considered%20a%20perfectly%20acceptable%20way%20to%20clean%20our%20dirtiest%20areas.%20We%20always%20wash%20our%20hands%20and%20bodies%20with%20water%2C%20why%20not%20wash%20our%20nether%20regions%20with%20water%20as%20well%3F%20This%20is%20where%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-bidet%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20bidet%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20provide%20a%20hygienic%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20word%20%3Cem%3Ebidet%3C%2Fem%3E%20comes%20from%20the%20French%20word%20for%20%26quot%3Blittle%20horse%26quot%3B%20because%20of%20how%20you%20straddle%20the%20original%20standalone%20bidets.%20At%20their%20most%20basic%2C%20bidets%20spray%20water%20to%20clean%20you%20more%20thoroughly%20after%20using%20the%20bathroom.%20High-end%20models%20will%20also%20air%20dry%20you%20off%20and%20feature%20heated%20seats%2C%20precise%20water%20heat%20and%20nozzle%20adjustments%2C%20and%20even%20nightlights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBidets%20are%20quite%20popular%20in%20France.%20You%20will%20also%20find%20them%20throughout%20Europe%2C%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20and%20in%20several%20Asian%20countries%2C%20including%20South%20Korea%20and%20Japan.%20Americans%20are%20just%20starting%20to%20catch%20on%20to%20the%20common%20sense%20benefits%20of%20bidet%20use.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229c7300e7-dfe0-43be-815a-a5cb45d86e1d%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Benefits%20of%20using%20bidets%5C%22%3EBenefits%20of%20using%20bidets%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBetter%20personal%20hygiene.%20Experts%20suggest%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Flifeandstyle%2Fshortcuts%2F2018%2Ffeb%2F11%2Fthe-bottom-line-why-its-time-the-bidet-made-a-comeback%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecleaning%20with%20toilet%20paper%20and%20water%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20much%20better%20for%20you%20than%20cleaning%20with%20toilet%20paper%20alone.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EEasier%20cleaning.%20For%20many%20people%20with%20mobility%20issues%2C%20it's%20hard%20to%20reach%20down%20there%20and%20clean%20up%20with%20toilet%20paper.%20With%20a%20bidet%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Facademic.oup.com%2Fgerontologist%2Farticle%2F45%2F5%2F694%2F652615%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eit's%20much%20easier%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EEco-friendliness.%20Bidet%20use%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.scientificamerican.com%2Farticle%2Fearth-talks-bidets%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emuch%20better%20for%20the%20environment%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20using%20paper%20made%20from%20trees.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EReduced%20risk%20of%20plumbing%20issues.%20With%20less%20toilet%20paper%20going%20through%20your%20pipes%2C%20there's%20a%20reduced%20chance%20of%20clogging.%20This%20is%20especially%20true%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.today.com%2Fseries%2Fone-small-thing%2Fare-flushable-wipes-really-flushable-t151945%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eif%20you%20use%20flushable%20wipes%20too%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsing%20a%20bidet%20may%20seem%20intimidating%20at%20first.%20We%20recommend%20starting%20with%20the%20lowest%20water%20pressure%20you%20can%20until%20you%20are%20comfortable.%20But%2C%20as%20you%20get%20used%20to%20the%20bidet's%20functions%2C%20you'll%20likely%20become%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20us%26quot%3B%20and%20wonder%20how%20you%20ever%20lived%20without%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fb4513ff-3925-4222-9f10-a297c74dffcd%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20to%20use%20any%20type%20of%20bidet%C2%A0%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20use%20any%20type%20of%20bidet%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22615%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Brondell%20Swash%201400%20bidet%20on%20a%20toilet%20in%20a%20bathroom%20with%20white%20interior%20features.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5e724a51c48540342d171254%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22461%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EWalmart%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBidet%20toilet%20seats%20and%20bidet%20attachments%20are%20the%20most%20common%20types%20of%20bidets%20you%20will%20encounter%20in%20American%20homes%2C%20and%20they%20essentially%20function%20the%20same.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fhow-to-install-a-bidet-toilet-seat%5C%22%20data-stringify-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fhow-to-install-a-bidet-toilet-seat%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%20data-sk%3D%5C%22tooltip_parent%5C%22%3ETo%20install%20a%20bidet%20toilet%20seat%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%C2%A0you%20just%20remove%20your%20current%20toilet%20seat%2C%20mount%20the%20bidet%2C%20connect%20it%20to%20your%20toilet's%20water%20supply%2C%20and%20let%20it%20work%20its%20magic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20bidet%20toilet%20seat%20and%20attachment%20I've%20used%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I've%20used%20quite%20a%20few%20%E2%80%94%20has%20had%20clearly%20labeled%20controls.%20However%2C%20the%20buttons%20or%20knobs%20can%20be%20hard%20to%20read%20while%20you%20are%20sitting%20on%20the%20toilet%20so%20you%20may%20want%20to%20take%20a%20moment%20to%20familiarize%20yourself%20with%20the%20controls%20before%20you%20do%20your%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229c505287-5949-4964-b683-b659cac348fa%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20to%20use%20an%20electric%20bidet%20seat%C2%A0%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20use%20an%20electric%20bidet%20seat%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElectric%20bidets%20usually%20have%20buttons%20on%20a%20side%20control%20panel%20or%20remote%20control.%20The%20number%20of%20options%20can%20seem%20overwhelming%20at%20first%2C%20but%20don't%20be%20afraid%20to%20experiment.%20For%20standard%20cleaning%2C%20you%20typically%20press%20the%20%26quot%3Bwash%26quot%3B%20or%20sometimes%20%26quot%3Brear%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bfront%26quot%3B%20button%2C%20depending%20on%20whether%20you're%20cleaning%20your%20front%20area%20or%20hindquarters.%20Commonly%2C%20there's%20also%20a%20nozzle%20position%20button%20that%20lets%20you%20adjust%20the%20position%20of%20the%20nozzle%20so%20the%20water%20goes%20precisely%20where%20you%20want%20it.%20As%20with%20the%20non-electric%20version%2C%20you'll%20find%20a%20button%20that%20adjusts%20the%20water%20temperature%20and%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20long%20you%20run%20the%20water%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20personal%20preference.%20I've%20found%20spraying%20for%2020%20to%2060%20seconds%20is%20enough%20to%20get%20the%20job%20done.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFancier%20bidet%20toilet%20seats%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20my%20favorite%20which%20I%20mentioned%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbrondell-swash-1400-bidet-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBrondell%20Swash%201400%20bidet%20review%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20have%20an%20array%20of%20other%20features%2C%20including%20adjustable%20spray%20width%2C%20an%20oscillating%20nozzle%2C%20a%20heated%20seat%2C%20a%20nightlight%2C%20and%20drying.%20If%20your%20bidet%20dries%20you%2C%20you%20might%20be%20able%20to%20get%20away%20with%20not%20using%20toilet%20paper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20instructions%20above%20will%20help%20you%20use%20the%20most%20popular%20bidet%20types%20in%20America%2C%20including%20toilets%20with%20built-in%20bidets%2C%20but%20you%20may%20also%20encounter%20a%20few%20other%20types.%C2%A0%20If%20you%20are%20looking%20to%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%2F%2Fplatform.twitter.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22twitter%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-conversation%3D%5C%22undefined%5C%22%20data-cards%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%20%E2%80%94Business%20Insider%20(%40businessinsider)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmims%2Fstatuses%2F1182084326864883713%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2010%2C%202019%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c03e6b9e-0dbd-49e9-884c-739bcf0198f7%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20to%20use%20a%20non-electric%20bidet%20seat%C2%A0%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20use%20a%20non-electric%20bidet%20seat%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENon-electric%20bidet%20seats%2C%20like%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20nofollow%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiipf_031920_how-to-use-a-bidet-20%26h%3D0d767bc42e523ca6d09c70858bb2074e44a7d5752e1c6f2816754939647b4fee%26postID%3D61b8efc7f2a36b1ac9f42cb0%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fhow-to-use-bidet%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fshareasale.com%252Fr.cfm%253Fb%253D999%2526amp%253Bu%253D1088116%2526amp%253Bm%253D64648%2526amp%253Burllink%253Dhellotushy.com%25252Fproducts%25252Fclassic-affordable-bidet%25253Fsscid%25253D31k4_dxlo2%252526utm_source%25253Dshareasale%252526utm_medium%25253Daffiliate%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETushy%20Classic%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20typically%20have%20a%20knob%20that%20you%20turn%20to%20release%20the%20water.%20The%20more%20you%20turn%20the%20knob%2C%20the%20more%20water%20pressure%20you%20will%20experience.%20Turn%20the%20knob%20slowly%20at%20first%20to%20avoid%20discomfort.%20While%20high-pressure%20water%20tends%20to%20do%20a%20better%20job%20of%20cleaning%2C%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20hurt%20yourself%20as%20the%20pressure%20can%20get%20intense.%20The%20folks%20at%20Tushy%20made%20their%20products%20super%20friendly%20since%20the%20attachment%20fits%20on%20your%20current%20toilet%20seat.%20If%20you%20need%20more%20convincing%20be%20sure%20to%20check%20out%20our%20full%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Ftushy-bidet-attachment-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETushy%20bidet%20attachment%20review%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENon-electric%20bidets%20may%20also%20have%20knobs%20for%20water%20temperature%20(usually%20just%20hot%20or%20cold)%20and%20nozzle%20position.%20You%20can%20experiment%20with%20these%20to%20achieve%20your%20optimal%20comfort%20level.%20Though%2C%20be%20careful%20with%20the%20hot%20water%20%E2%80%94%20it%20does%20a%20superior%20job%20of%20cleaning%20but%20there's%20the%20potential%20of%20scalding.%20That%20said%2C%20I've%20never%20hurt%20myself%20with%20water%20pressure%20or%20hot%20water%20when%20using%20a%20bidet%20seat.%20It's%20possible%20but%20unlikely.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224e42f38f-0422-413f-8386-60427705b26d%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20to%20use%20a%20handheld%20bidet%20sprayer%C2%A0%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20use%20a%20handheld%20bidet%20sprayer%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBidet%20sprayers%20connect%20to%20your%20toilet's%20water%20source%20and%20work%20essentially%20the%20same%20as%20a%20sprayer%20you%20might%20have%20on%20your%20kitchen%20sink%20or%20in%20your%20garden.%20After%20you're%20done%20doing%20your%20business%2C%20you%20grab%20the%20sprayer%20while%20still%20sitting%20on%20the%20toilet%2C%20point%20it%20at%20the%20area%20you%20want%20to%20clean%2C%20and%20squeeze%20the%20handle.%20The%20water%20and%20debris%20should%20go%20into%20the%20toilet.%20You%20can%20also%20adjust%20the%20amount%20of%20water%20pressure.%20We%20recommend%20beginning%20with%20low%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221312e4e1-bbb1-4b13-929c-82a72778772e%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20to%20use%20a%20portable%20or%20travel%20bidet%C2%A0%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20use%20a%20portable%20or%20travel%20bidet%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20I%20started%20living%20the%20bidet%20life%2C%20it%20was%20hard%20for%20me%20to%20travel%20since%20none%20of%20the%20places%20I%20went%20to%20had%20bidets.%20So%2C%20I%20picked%20up%20a%20travel%20bidet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%20called%20a%20portable%20bidet%2C%20travel%20bidets%20consist%20of%20a%20bottle%20that%20holds%20about%2013%20ounces%20of%20water%20and%20a%20screw-on%20nozzle.%20You%20fill%20the%20bottle%20with%20warm%20%E2%80%94%20but%20not%20too%20hot%20%E2%80%94%20water%2C%20screw%20on%20the%20nozzle%2C%20and%20when%20you%20are%20done%20using%20the%20bathroom%2C%20point%20the%20nozzle%20at%20the%20area%20you%20want%20to%20clean%20while%20still%20sitting%20on%20the%20toilet%20and%20squeeze%20the%20bottle.%20This%20will%20send%20a%20stream%20of%20water%20to%20clean.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20a%20bigger%20person%2C%20like%20me%2C%20you%20may%20need%20to%20lean%20to%20one%20side%20while%20on%20the%20toilet%20so%20that%20you%20have%20room%20to%20get%20the%20nozzle%20down%20there.%20And%2C%20when%20you're%20done%2C%20don't%20forget%20to%20thoroughly%20rinse%20the%20bidet%20in%20the%20sink%20before%20washing%20your%20hands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20are%20looking%20for%20an%20affordable%20bidet%20under%20%2415%2C%20check%20out%20our%20full%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbrondell-gospa-travel-bidet-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBrondell%20Gospa%20travel%20bidet%20review%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222dfbe02c-b5be-4d5e-bbc7-f31fcc362edb%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20to%20use%20a%20standalone%20bidet%C2%A0%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20use%20a%20standalone%20bidet%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStandalone%20bidets%20are%20the%20original%20bidets.%20They%20are%20usually%20made%20of%20ceramic%20and%20resemble%20a%20toilet%20without%20a%20lid%20or%20reservoir.%20Standalone%20bidets%20are%20typically%20positioned%20next%20to%20toilets%20since%20you%20use%20them%20after%20urinating%20or%20defecating.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20use%20a%20standalone%20bidet%2C%20you%20can%20sit%20or%20straddle%20the%20bidet%20facing%20the%20fixtures%20(you%20may%20need%20to%20take%20your%20pants%20off%20for%20this)%20or%20away%20from%20the%20fixtures%20(like%20a%20toilet).%20Make%20sure%20you%20position%20yourself%20over%20the%20jet%2C%20then%20turn%20the%20knobs%20to%20release%20hot%20or%20cold%20water%20depending%20on%20what%20you%20are%20most%20comfortable%20with.%20We%20recommend%20starting%20with%20cold%20water%20and%20slowly%20adding%20hot%20to%20avoid%20the%20chance%20of%20scalding.%20Move%20your%20position%20to%20ensure%20you%20wash%20the%20parts%20you%20want%20to%20clean.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20standalone%20bidets%20don't%20have%20jets.%20Instead%2C%20they%20simply%20fill%20the%20basin%2C%20and%20you%20are%20supposed%20to%20use%20your%20hand%20to%20lap%20the%20water%20over%20your%20dirty%20areas%20as%20you%20might%20in%20the%20bath%20or%20shower.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226a240a47-93d2-4d25-a1e5-2a8f3615d8bb%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Do%20you%20still%20need%20toilet%20paper%3F%5C%22%3EDo%20you%20still%20need%20toilet%20paper%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224026%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22toilet%20