%20with%20remarkable%20strength.%20Mum%20always%20told%20us%20to%20never%20lose%20hope%20and%20to%20find%20something%20positive%20even%20in%20the%20worst%20of%20times.%20Those%20words%20carried%20us%20through.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20that%20time%2C%20I%20was%20pursuing%20nursing%20training.%20Financially%2C%20we%20survived%20with%20the%20small%20savings%20left%20by%20our%20parents%20and%20by%20renting%20out%20a%20few%20rooms%20in%20the%20house.%20We%20were%20careful%20not%20to%20waste%20any%20amount%20from%20life%20insurance%20because%20we%20knew%20once%20that%20money%20was%20gone%2C%20it%20would%20never%20return%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%2025-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERupam%20too%20refused%20to%20compromise%20on%20her%20studies.%20%E2%80%9CI%20realised%20very%20early%20that%20financial%20independence%20is%20the%20only%20weapon%20for%20a%20girl%20in%20such%20a%20society%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20fund%20her%20education%2C%20she%20began%20tutoring%20students%20from%20Class%202%20to%20Class%2011.%20Every%20day%2C%20she%20woke%20at%204%20am%20to%20study%2C%20then%20travelled%2080%20kilometres%20from%20Kunti%20to%20Ranchi%20for%20her%20college.%20By%20afternoon%2C%20she%20was%20back%20home%2C%20and%20from%204%20pm%20to%207%20pm%2C%20she%20taught%20neighbourhood%20children.%20Only%20after%20dinner%20would%20she%20return%20to%20her%20books%2C%20often%20studying%20late%20into%20the%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20used%20to%20study%20six%20to%20eight%20hours%20daily%2C%20mostly%20at%20dawn%20and%20late%20at%20night%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rupam%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20lockdown%20years%20were%20actually%20a%20blessing%20because%20I%20could%20save%20travel%20time%20and%20focus%20completely%20on%20strengthening%20my%20base.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20journey%20was%20far%20from%20smooth.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F495179%2Fsubhankar-bala-ia