erindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fonam-2_11zon-1757051553-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fonam-2_11zon-1757051553-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fonam-2_11zon-1757051553-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-496739%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EKummatti%20Kali%20%3C%2Fem%3Eadds%20whimsy%20to%20Onam%2C%20with%20dancers%20wearing%20wooden%20masks%20and%20colourful%20grass%20skirts.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFolk%20songs%3A%20%3Cem%3EOnappaattu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20Onam%2C%20the%20air%20is%20filled%20with%20the%20melodies%20of%20centuries-old%20folk%20songs.%20Known%20as%20%3Cem%3EOnappaattu%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20these%20songs%20are%20both%20celebratory%20and%20nostalgic%2C%20offering%20a%20lyrical%20glimpse%20into%20Kerala%E2%80%99s%20agrarian%20way%20of%20life.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETraditionally%20sung%20by%20women%2C%20they%20evoke%20themes%20of%20bountiful%20harvests%2C%20the%20joy%20of%20togetherness%2C%20and%20reflections%20on%20community%20and%20tradition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EOnappaattu%20%3C%2Fem%3Eoften%20accompanies%20the%20making%20of%20%3Cem%3EPookalams%20%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%94%20the%20intricate%20flower%20carpets%20that%20adorn%20homes%20and%20symbolise%20harmony.%20As%20much%20as%20Onam%20is%20celebrated%20through%20rituals%20and%20feasts%2C%20it%20truly%20comes%20alive%20in%20the%20symphony%20of%20voices%20that%20echo%20across%20villages%20and%20towns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EVallamkali%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%20The%20magnificent%20boat%20races%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20spectacle%20of%20speed%2C%20synchrony%2C%20and%20spirit%2C%20the%20snake%20boat%20races%20%E2%80%94%20or%20%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EVallamkali%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E